Dancer and influencer Janemena has explained how she s been able to build up her page over the years. The social media personality via series of post on her insta story reminded her critics that she built her page with her ‘backside’ contrary to what they claim. According to Mrs Plies, incessant trolls and appearances on blogs for varying reasons didn’t contribute to the growth of her page.   Gunmen kill 11, injure many in Southern Kaduna     PHOTOS: Dignitaries bid Late Head of State Shonekan farewell     Ekiti farmers appeal to Fayemi on insecurity   She said her 3.9million Instagram followers were amassed based on the contents she provide them with by making dance video where she shakes her behind. - Advertisement - She also vowed to continue her trade even if she eventually happens into billions adding, it’s no one’s business. “I never built my page by being on people’s blogs every second. I built my page with my nyansh o. Lol not yours and I will shake it even if Im swimming in billions forever and it’s nobody’ s business,” she wrote.